{"tid":1136321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"百萬富翁突破100萬人 6.8萬港人擁千萬身家","createTime":"2019-05-03T02:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T11:14:02.000Z","uid":113626,"like":8,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"2d0cac538ba79ba32acd592c3fce688d40709f44","tid":1136321,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:31:03.000Z","msg":"簡單d講就係除左樓, 其他資產都計係流動資產 (例如現金, 股票, 債券), 所以講咩d人有棟樓已經幾百萬, 樓係唔計.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1171044/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1171044%2F&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=137152b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1171044%2F&h=1ddf4555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1171044/</a><br />\n<br />\n花旗銀行發表香港千萬富翁調查報告。<span style=\"color: red;\">去年本港有6.8萬名擁有1000萬港元或以上流動資產的富裕人士，按年增加一成半。</span><span style=\"color: red;\">去年另新增20多萬名百萬富翁，令人數突破100萬人，升至100.8萬人，</span><span style=\"color: red;\">按此推算，即每7位港人便有1個百萬富翁。</span><br />\n<br />\n花旗銀行去年9月至11月，委託香港大學社會科學研究中心訪問4139人。在6.8萬千萬富翁中，流動資產分布以現金及存款為主，佔36%，其次是股票，佔27%，當中84%擁有本地物業。<br />\n<br />\n調查同時於去年9月至今年2月，訪問約200名內地富翁。結果發現，兩地千萬富翁收入來源明顯不同。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">本地千萬富翁的收入來源，55%來自薪酬，20%來自生意，17%來自投資，5%來自遺產</span>；內地富翁收入來源主要來自生意，佔55%，其次是投資，僅8%來自工作。調查另發現，僅4%香港富翁對創業感興趣，相反內地有50%對創業有興趣。"},{"pid":"aba9a4da2a5534b43b3cb5eee63545a877e237f6","tid":1136321,"uid":20362,"like":193,"dislike":3,"score":190,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:36:12.000Z","msg":"富翁....???"},{"pid":"a437df5f7d2f2abb5286618ca3f1d638a9172ad2","tid":1136321,"uid":11719,"like":201,"dislike":1,"score":200,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:38:49.000Z","msg":"100萬港幣四分之一層樓都買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfd15829d1cbac5e45cd9e8ac53f8972d14a1a3","tid":1136321,"uid":50502,"like":94,"dislike":3,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:41:39.000Z","msg":"好出奇咩 今時今日準備買樓既實有100 萬揸手做首期<br />\n廿年前班人一早full paid哂 full paid 完儲幾年就有100 萬啦<br />\n同一班人 叻既搵得多/ 入政府跳pt 輕鬆十萬月入<br />\n再以當時首期幾十萬一間屋 入幾間 再放 咁就千幾萬cash"},{"pid":"3a0163df523d726dc8a4a53ec222a2bddcbba3c2","tid":1136321,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":43,"score":-41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:43:30.000Z","msg":"以為係自己<br />\n原來講緊流動資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b71f43771b67274d68eeb39b7bc7381df6f40d8","tid":1136321,"uid":224510,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:44:46.000Z","msg":"得果百萬撚係富翁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c10efc6224a7d8870639b67b8b2fa32bc7f3cb","tid":1136321,"uid":79077,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:12:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e25800c02191b1861f6fcf360d1344786241dd26","tid":1136321,"uid":203983,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bea4c734a0c8eecb3654d39147dd3ac09f3fe40d","tid":1136321,"uid":78016,"like":114,"dislike":3,"score":111,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:16:20.000Z","msg":"millionaire 個 million 應該係講緊 us dollar<br />\n即係有780萬港紙先叫 millionaire<br />\n唔通揸 100萬台幣又millionaire<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48614e425ac180233df7c54238fae14e8a4479a1","tid":1136321,"uid":224479,"like":15,"dislike":6,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:17:35.000Z","msg":"100萬太易 <br />\n1000萬就難"},{"pid":"0c4f20590b7f6789226c06bc67edc446232c890b","tid":1136321,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"窮撚點都翻唔到身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n翻身起碼要兩三代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論幾努力都好 除非你真係好勁好專業<br />\n收入去到醫生咁既level"},{"pid":"a576023f707f61c9a214e344e81f